events.name: Kansas Jayhawks at Coastal Carolina Chanticleers

headlines.description: — Reese White ran for 102 yards and three touchdowns, Grayson McCall threw for two scores and ran for a third and No. 17 Coastal Carolina beat Kansas for the third straight season, 49-22 on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: No. 17 Coastal Carolina wins third staight over Kansas 49-22

UTEP Miners at Boise State Broncos

headlines.description: — Hank Bachmeier threw for 340 yards and two touchdowns, and Stefan Cobbs added a special teams touchdown and a 61-yard scoring reception as Boise State defeated UTEP 54-13 Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Bachmeier, Cobbs lead Boise State past UTEP, 54-13
